1093
00:54:00,633 --> 00:54:04,871
That's not a very positive
picture of the future.

1094
00:54:04,904 --> 00:54:06,706
Why should anyone believe you?

1095
00:54:08,941 --> 00:54:10,576
Because they know it's true.

1096
