1104
00:54:41,306 --> 00:54:42,307
Now he can't.

1105
00:54:44,409 --> 00:54:46,746
Time will tell if
they ever come to their senses.

1106
00:54:47,412 --> 00:54:49,347
History will be their judge.

1107
00:54:51,349 --> 00:54:52,618
Let's hope they do.

1108
00:54:54,520 --> 00:54:57,422
If the President
was so dangerous,

1109
00:54:57,457 --> 00:55:00,392
why not travel back to
the time before he got elected

1110
00:55:00,425 --> 00:55:02,260
and stop it
before he got started?

1111
00:55:02,294 --> 00:55:05,330
We debated that,
but in the end,

1112
00:55:05,363 --> 00:55:07,533
we realized he could
serve a purpose.

1113
00:55:07,867 --> 00:55:10,368
It could be a wake-up
call to the world.

1114
00:55:11,003 --> 00:55:14,674
Kind of like the bombing
of Nagasaki and Hiroshima.

1115
00:55:14,707 --> 00:55:19,011
We thought if you could get
a glimpse of the destruction

1116
00:55:19,045 --> 00:55:21,013
he could cause
with the power of

1117
00:55:21,047 --> 00:55:23,716
the United States presidency,
you might work more diligently

1118
00:55:23,750 --> 00:55:25,852
to see that it would
never happen again.

1119
00:55:25,885 --> 00:55:28,588
With him gone,
we hope the world will realize

1120
00:55:28,621 --> 00:55:30,623
what it almost lost
and work harder

1121
00:55:30,656 --> 00:55:32,692
to achieve positive things.

1122
00:55:32,725 --> 00:55:34,927
We hope it unleashes
a wave of goodwill

1123
00:55:34,961 --> 00:55:37,530
and optimism and cooperation.

1124
00:55:37,563 --> 00:55:41,299
We hope the world unites
instead of divides.

1125
00:55:43,603 --> 00:55:44,704
It has to.

1126
00:55:45,738 --> 00:55:47,640
Our future is at stake.

1127
00:55:50,543 --> 00:55:53,079
Near the end of the
prosecution's case,

1128
00:55:53,112 --> 00:55:55,014
you stated that
you wanted to change

1129
00:55:55,047 --> 00:55:57,550
your plea to self-defense.

1130
00:55:58,484 --> 00:56:00,586
Can you explain
what you meant by that?

1131
00:56:00,620 --> 00:56:03,456
My world was being destroyed
because of his actions.

1132
00:56:03,956 --> 00:56:06,793
My family was destroyed
because of his actions.

1133
00:56:06,826 --> 00:56:10,496
I was about to be destroyed
because of his actions.

1134
00:56:10,863 --> 00:56:12,899
How were you
about to be destroyed?

1135
00:56:12,932 --> 00:56:14,033
I'm a scientist.

1136
00:56:15,034 --> 00:56:17,003
I was charged with being
an enemy of the people.

1137
00:56:18,004 --> 00:56:19,739
It's a charge he perfected.

1138
00:56:19,772 --> 00:56:21,507
Was he still president?

1139
00:56:21,908 --> 00:56:23,509
No.

1140
00:56:23,543 --> 00:56:25,343
He died 20 years ago
in my world.

1141
00:56:25,711 --> 00:56:29,982
But his son took over and was
even more destructive and vile.

1142
00:56:32,552 --> 00:56:34,854
When lies become the truth

1143
00:56:35,922 --> 00:56:38,524
and the truth becomes lies,

1144
00:56:40,059 --> 00:56:41,627
democracy dies.

1145
00:56:42,862 --> 00:56:46,899
He was on the verge of
killing democracy forever.

1146
00:56:46,933 --> 00:56:48,534
And if that happened,
the world as you know

1147
00:56:48,568 --> 00:56:50,136
it would cease to exist

1148
00:56:50,169 --> 00:56:52,471
and the world I grew up
in would be born.

1149
00:56:52,505 --> 00:56:54,707
A world where science
is considered a cult

1150
00:56:54,740 --> 00:56:57,109
and those who practice it
are subject to termination.

1151
00:56:58,044 --> 00:56:59,745
What do you mean
by termination?

1152
00:56:59,779 --> 00:57:01,413
Shot on sight.

1153
00:57:02,048 --> 00:57:04,116
I don't understand,
why scientists?

1154
00:57:05,785 --> 00:57:07,854
Scientists predicted
the devastating role

1155
00:57:07,887 --> 00:57:10,422
a changing
climate could have on Earth.

1156
00:57:10,456 --> 00:57:11,991
It came true.

1157
00:57:12,024 --> 00:57:13,893
Your president
called it a hoax.

1158
00:57:13,926 --> 00:57:15,728
It was easier to believe that

1159
00:57:15,761 --> 00:57:17,964
it was a hoax than to do
something to try to stop it.

1160
00:57:17,997 --> 00:57:20,066
So when it came true,

1161
00:57:20,099 --> 00:57:21,601
it had to be discounted.

1162
00:57:21,634 --> 00:57:23,069
The best way to discount it

1163
00:57:23,102 --> 00:57:25,671
is to discount the
messengers of truth.

1164
00:57:25,705 --> 00:57:27,573
We were targeted for removal.

1165
00:57:27,940 --> 00:57:30,910
To survive,
science was forced underground.

1166
00:57:31,477 --> 00:57:32,979
Both my parents
were scientists,

1167
00:57:33,012 --> 00:57:34,580
they were leaders
in their field.

1168
00:57:34,614 --> 00:57:36,182
My mother graduated
from Harvard

1169
00:57:36,215 --> 00:57:37,984
with a PhD in astrophysics.

1170
00:57:38,017 --> 00:57:39,652
