1175
00:57:53,065 --> 00:57:54,734
Do you know what it's like

1176
00:57:54,767 --> 00:57:57,103
to have your parents
just disappear?

1177
00:58:02,475 --> 00:58:03,876
What about you?

1178
00:58:04,944 --> 00:58:06,646
I was a concrete finisher.

1179
00:58:07,647 --> 00:58:09,148
And a scientist?

1180
00:58:09,181 --> 00:58:12,518
Yes.
