this man is charged
with committing.

1193
00:58:35,675 --> 00:58:36,742
So we will hear him out

1194
00:58:37,276 --> 00:58:40,046
as long as his testimony
is relevant to his defense.

1195
00:58:40,746 --> 00:58:42,515
And I suggest you do the same.

1196
00:58:42,548 --> 00:58:44,016
Unless he says something that

1197
00:58:44,050 --> 00:58:46,619
you have a legitimate
legal objection to.

1198
00:58:46,652 --> 00:58:47,853
It's just...

1199
00:58:47,887 --> 00:58:50,456
Yes, it is.

1200
00:58:51,891 --> 00:58:53,759
Please proceed, Mr. Johnson.

1201
00:58:53,793 --> 00:58:55,227
Thank you, Your Honor.

1202
00:58:55,261 --> 00:58:58,564
Um, you said that
you were targeted.

1203
00:58:59,598 --> 00:59:01,000
Was anyone else
