and eventually
journalists were terminated.

1208
00:59:12,678 --> 00:59:16,082
But they weren't
the first to go.

1209
00:59:16,849 --> 00:59:17,950
Who was first?

1210
00:59:19,652 --> 00:59:20,720
Attorneys.

1211
00:59:22,121 --> 00:59:23,923
Why attorneys?

1212
00:59:24,623 --> 00:59:26,792
To undermine the rule of law

1213
00:59:26,826 --> 00:59:28,894
and the media
helped fuel the fire.

1214
00:59:28,928 --> 00:59:31,964
