attorneys going to jail,

1215
00:59:31,998 --> 00:59:34,734
big ratings, and no one
stood up for them.

1216
00:59:35,134 --> 00:59:37,069
Once attorneys were gone,
journalists were next.

1217
00:59:37,103 --> 00:59:38,904
There were no attorneys left
to defend them.

1218
00:59:38,938 --> 00:59:41,607
Then scientists, then artists.

1219
00:59:42,608 --> 00:59:45,277
