or kill you for it.

1224
00:59:55,721 --> 00:59:56,922
Anyone.

1225
00:59:57,623 --> 01:00:01,627
So we live in constant
fear of our neighbors,

1226
01:00:01,660 --> 01:00:03,963
our coworkers, our friends,

1227
01:00:03,996 --> 01:00:06,532
anyone who's not a
part of the resistance.

1228
01:00:07,800 --> 01:00:09,335
Was there bounty on you?

1229
01:00:09,368 --> 01:00:10,770
Yes, of course.

1230
01:00:10,803 --> 01:00:11,871
How much?

1231
01:00:12,304 --> 01:00:15,875
In your world,
it would be about $50.

1232
01:00:15,908 --> 01:00:17,676
Fifty dollars?

1233
01:00:17,710 --> 01:00:19,211
When you cheapen
the value of life,

1234
01:00:19,245 --> 01:00:21,113
it becomes easier to destroy.

1235
01:00:21,947 --> 01:00:23,749
Everything is disposable.

1236
01:00:25,017 --> 01:00:26,786
The destruction
of your institutions

1237
01:00:26,819 --> 01:00:27,987
became a way of life.

1238
01:00:28,020 --> 01:00:30,022
Things like public education,

1239
01:00:30,256 --> 01:00:33,025
your intelligence,
and environmental agencies.

1240
01:00:33,059 --> 01:00:34,760
